{"id": 1042, "genre": 1001, "title": "你曾遭遇过哪些前功尽弃的悲伤经历？", "description": "那我之前所做的一切.....又是图的什么呢？（题目来自：Giselle Potter）", "record_count": 2887, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607031523131p4kwVNZeWdsl9n0.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-21T11:08:52Z", "options": [{"id": 91136, "content": "好笑又心疼 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 99994}, {"id": 91137, "content": "认真复习，结果记错了考试时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562262}, {"id": 91138, "content": "认真复习，结果记错了考试时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562262}, {"id": 91139, "content": "失恋", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652436}, {"id": 92931, "content": "想写折多写了一点变成了拆，约勾点越大?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632917}, {"id": 91653, "content": "考试最后一刻想到一个单词怎么写  少写最后一个字母交走了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654167}, {"id": 91143, "content": "想了很久的方案被老师毙了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 610536}, {"id": 91144, "content": "爱了很久的人，不爱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652442}, {"id": 91146, "content": "与好友约好时间，要出门了却下起暴雨", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647607}, {"id": 91660, "content": "等了半天公交车决定换步行走没多久发现那公交车从你旁边开走了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 174091}, {"id": 91662, "content": "两个字可以概括“所有”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640155}, {"id": 104207, "content": "减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700756}, {"id": 91153, "content": "吃西瓜，挖了一勺中间最好吃的部分，结果手滑掉地上了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652472}, {"id": 93713, "content": "多米诺骨牌，不小心碰到的那一刻，真是挺痛的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660788}, {"id": 91154, "content": "修改了好几次的短信最后还是没发出去", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641054}, {"id": 91155, "content": "复习好久的重难点被告知不在考试范围内:)", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 180193}, {"id": 91158, "content": "锻炼，增加肌肉。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598605}, {"id": 91160, "content": "考证书 每次都是报了名 最好没考到。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614327}, {"id": 91161, "content": "为了前任来到现在的城市上学，还没考试完就被劈腿了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652502}, {"id": 93209, "content": "很认真的看书 但是考试还是挂科了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166776}, {"id": 91162, "content": "复习的点都没考", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92714}, {"id": 91165, "content": "坚持去喜欢你", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642629}, {"id": 92701, "content": "高考啊……努力很久却并不尽人意", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 393100}, {"id": 91166, "content": "暧昧不明了很久 感觉马上云开雾散还是吹了 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579627}, {"id": 91167, "content": "99.9% 0kb/s", "image": null, "praise_count": 182, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637881}, {"id": 91679, "content": "跨专业考研复试挂了~~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237178}, {"id": 91168, "content": "恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115332}, {"id": 91169, "content": "研究了一只股票特别想买特别好，怎么看怎么激动，第二天直接停牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650393}, {"id": 98337, "content": "换新手机，把500多个联系人一一仔细分类输入，第二天连上电脑选择了同步…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680452}, {"id": 91178, "content": "恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269318}, {"id": 91179, "content": "由我作曲，伴奏，舞台导演，服装设计的节目表演却没有我，不提我", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 375176}, {"id": 91180, "content": "减肥，减了一半又全部反弹。我想拍死我自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652283}, {"id": 91181, "content": "曾经流行十字绣，那年我也买了，暗自下决心绣好之时就是嫁人的时候啦，如今五年了，还是放着了，然而还没有嫁人……", "image": "img/option/option/201607021828267V9T62xaScEJWqD1.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652542}, {"id": 91438, "content": "专业考试，三科都要上60，不然就要重考，然而已经连续3次有一科，59、58、59这种分，正在准备最新一次考试的我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653396}, {"id": 91183, "content": "哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632576}, {"id": 91184, "content": "耗费两个小时下的电影告诉我文件损坏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642603}, {"id": 91185, "content": "说了要忘记前任，结果不小心路过以前约会的地点，又忍不住进去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652566}, {"id": 91443, "content": "被分手不能往回", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539921}, {"id": 91188, "content": "用rational rose画图 保存的时候格式选错 之后就打不开了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 293232}, {"id": 91189, "content": "崩溃的PS，无需解释更多", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540072}, {"id": 91190, "content": "做好设计，然后没存，死机了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 538257}, {"id": 91191, "content": "减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652645}, {"id": 91192, "content": "努力了半天的事 没结果", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652654}, {"id": 91193, "content": "大概就是爱你罢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652674}, {"id": 91194, "content": "我就蹭蹭不进去", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652684}, {"id": 91195, "content": "减脂控糖，坚持不下去，偷吃碳水化合物。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 297241}, {"id": 91196, "content": "怎么计划今天总是被乱拉节奏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623183}, {"id": 91197, "content": "下载电影没电了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652721}, {"id": 91709, "content": "复制了内容，要粘贴的时候，又按了crtl+c", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654361}, {"id": 91199, "content": "升级哔哩哔哩会员答题，30题到处找答案答了29题时，我按了个F5....", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460062}]}